  "businessLogic": [
    "Check featureType from slotsDTO; if 'OpenAccount', invoke validateInputUsingRules.",
    "In validateInputUsingRules: parse DOMAIN_CURRENT_COMMAND_PAYLOAD into AccountDTO and set it as ACCOUNT_IDENTITY on slotsDTO; retrieve ReferenceContractDTO and if present set productType on slotsDTO.",
    "Insert slotsDTO and AccountDTO as facts into inputRules WorkingMemory, fire rules, and query 'queryInputField'; throw FbpValidationException for any failing validation result (ACCOUNT_CURRENCY, PURPOSE_ID, CIF_ID, DEPOSIT_PERIOD, DEPOSIT_AMOUNT, CREDIT_LIMIT, etc.).",
    "If featureType is 'FundTransfer' and DOMAIN_CURRENT_COMMAND_PAYLOAD is not null, invoke validateTransferRules: parse payload into TransferDTO, set as TRANSFER_DETAILS, insert into transferRules WorkingMemory, fire rules, query 'queryResponse', and throw FbpValidationException for any failing result (TRANSACTION_LINES, TRANSFER_AMOUNT, CURRENCY, LINE_ACCOUNT_ID, LINE_TYPE, CURRENCY_MISMATCH, TRANSFER_AMOUNT_UNBALANCED, LINE_CURRENCY).",
    "If featureType is 'MultiCreditTransaction' and DOMAIN_CURRENT_COMMAND_PAYLOAD is not null, invoke validateMultiCreditRules: parse payload into MultiCreditTransactionDTO, set as MULTI_CREDIT_DETAILS, insert into multiCreditDebitSessions, fire rules, query 'queryResponse', and handle validation result via handleMultiTxnValidationResult.",
    "If featureType is 'MultiDebitTransaction' and DOMAIN_CURRENT_COMMAND_PAYLOAD is not null, invoke validateMultiDebitRules: parse payload into MultiDebitTransactionDTO, set as MULTI_DEBIT_DETAILS, insert into multiCreditDebitSessions, fire rules, query 'queryResponse', and handle validation result via handleMultiTxnValidationResult.",
    "handleMultiTxnValidationResult throws FbpValidationException for TRANSACTION_LINES, TXN_AMOUNT, TXN_CURRENCY, TXN_VALUE_DATE, TXN_ACCOUNT_NUMBER, ALL_LINES_MUST_BE_CREDIT, ALL_LINES_MUST_BE_DEBIT.",
    "If featureType is 'AccountClosure', retrieve AccountClosureDTO from DOMAIN_REQUEST, insert slotsDTO and closureDTO into inputRules WorkingMemory, fire rules, query 'queryInputField', and throw FbpValidationException if result is ':ACCOUNT_NUMBER'.",
    "If featureType is 'TDAccountPreClosure', retrieve TDAccountPreClosureDTO from DOMAIN_REQUEST, insert slotsDTO and preClosureDTO into inputRules WorkingMemory, fire rules, query 'queryInputField', and throw FbpValidationException if result is ':ACCOUNT_NUMBER'."
  ],
